1000.text: I'll keep on being the class presideeent!

1007.text: A new record! The peak of Sakura season!

1087.text: Set your back as straight as a line!

2030.text: I'll keep on being the class presideeent!

2032.text: The sincerest of thank you's for your guidance!

2033.text: Proper breathing, proper condition! And, of course, it's proper that I win!

2034.text: I'm in flawless shape for this race! Truly, I'm the greatest! It's almost as if I've already won!

2035.text: The sincerest of thank you's for your guidance!

10000.text: This I swear! Under your guidance, I will become worthy of being an exemplary role model for all Umamusume… I shall become the greatest class president there ever was!

10001.text: There is never error in Trainer's guidance! Why?…Because you're my Trainer!

10002.text: My cellphone has been fully charged! Now, no matter when, where, or how I get lost, I can contact you, Trainer!

10003.text: This year's resolution is Ba・ku・shin! I've had it decided since New Year's Day last year!

10004.text: While cooking, the chocolate I was making… blew up. I guess it just couldn't withstand my explosively passionate feelings!

10005.text: For Trainer, who has a mature palate! I have prepared for you bitter chocolate that has been burnt to a crisp, therefore making it extra dark! Fufuu―n!

10006.text: …Faster, faster, faster! Now, I command you to shoot now, shooting star! My wish has been sufficiently prepared!!

10007.text: Trick-or-treaaaaat! Huh? Nothing happened? I heard if you recite those magic words, you'll get free candy…

10008.text: Let's enjoy Christmas to the very fullest! I'm the one who takes the initiative to organize all the holiday events, because it's the class president's duty!

10009.text: Trainer, did you know? Santa is extreeemely fast. So fast that he eludes me…!

10010.text: Lots of cleaning to do?! Leave it to me! If you just throw away all the stuff lying on the floor, it'll make most places look great!

10011.text: It's your birthday, so please take care of yourself, kick back, and relax! I have the utmost confidence in myself not to break anything today!

10012.text: A very happy birthday to you, Trainer! I see… the fact that you have aged superbly! (Clapclapclap!)

10013.text: Today is the fateful day I was born! I wouldn't have any objections if you decided to make it a national holiday!

10014.text: Ehehe… My dad and mom wished me a happy birthday earlier… To tell you the truth, I'm on cloud nine right now!

10015.text: It seems like there's some news! It might have something to do with my class! Let's check it out!

10016.text: It seems a present has arrived! Could it be, a gift from someone who caught wind of our spectacular efforts?

10017.text: It looks like you've completed a goal! I'm quite proud of myself, too! Ehhen!

10018.text: Ohh… It looks like there's an event going on. Which class president made the necessary provisions… I must investigate this.

10019.text: It's quite lively, isn't it… Doing something fun without the authorization of the class president… Uuuu～… Please let me join iiin!

10021.text: Well done! Trainer, your directory level has gone up!

20000.text: Even if my energy is almost exhausted… I'll stay strong… As an example for everyone… I… will… keep……running!

20001.text: U, uuughh… Move, legs, mooove～!! Why are you so heavyyy―?!

20002.text: A role model for students everywhere! I shall show you all my magnificent training!!

20003.text: Please expect nothing but the biggest of Bakushins! Today, I'm giving it my aaaaalll!!

20004.text: No matter the training, this Bakushin O right here will show you how it's done!

20005.text: Warm-up has been flawlessly completed! Now, now, which training shall we do?!

20007.text: I see, it's training time! Roger that!

20009.text: Haah～… The sky is beautiful as always today, isn't it～…

20010.text: Uuuugh… As class representative… As president… I know what I must do, buuuut…!

20021.text: A race, right?…I'm fine! Even if I don't have the same lightning in my legs… I can still do it…!

20022.text: …Traaain… errrr… A-are we doing another raaace…? As you may have anticipated, I have to say, I want a breaaak…

20023.text: I can feel it! The passionate gazes of those who want to cheer on the class president staring at me! I shall answer the call and meet your expectations!

20024.text: No matter who your opponent is, Bakushin all the way! Though looks may be deceiving, in truth I am overflowing with confidence!

20025.text: I'm in flawless shape for this race! Truly, I'm the greatest! It's almost as if I've already won!

20026.text: I shall put my heart and soul into every sprint! No matter the race, I refuse to cut corners!

20027.text: Right now, I'm faster than anyone else! In other words, business as usual!

20028.text: Proper breathing, proper condition! And, of course, it's proper that I win!

20029.text: If it's a speed showdown, I won't lose it!

20030.text: Most assuredly, I promise you victory!

20031.text: May I start running now? I may, right?!

20032.text: Hmhmhm… My legs have started trembling the tiiiiniest bit. Perhaps these are the "nerves" that everyone's been feeling.

20033.text: …I Bakushin-ed without thinking! It'll be fine, we'll win for sure!

20034.text: There's no need to worry. Because I shall blow everyone away and leave the opposition in the dust for you!

20035.text: …Yesterday, I dreamt I came in last place. But, a dream is just a dream… right?!

20036.text: No matter the predicament I find myself in, I have a secret to coming in first place. That secret is…speed!!

20037.text: I understand being scared. But, the fastest wins… and that is the simple, eternal truth!

20050.text: The sincerest of thank you's for your guidance!

20051.text: Oooh―! I'll give it my best shot!

30000.text: Indeeed. Just as expected, I'm superb!

30001.text: Hmhm… It seems I still have everyone's undying admiration!

30002.text: Everyone else was fast, too! Let us acknowledge this!

30005.text: Because I'm an honor student! Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha―!

30007.text: Because I'm an honor student! Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha―!

60000.text: I'm counting on you for a class president-inspired cheer, please and thank you!

60001.text: I shall demonstrate to you how to put on the most superior of Lives!

70000.text: Let's do our very best! No need to worry, I am here!

70001.text: Meeting me must have been a moment of divine destiny for you! Fufu!

70004.text: The school uniform suits me better than anyone else! You guessed it, because I'm the class president!

70008.text: …Indeed! An outfit worthy of being worn by the star of the class!

70009.text: No matter the race… Let's make the Sakura blossoms bloom!

70010.text: School uniforms are sacred garments! I fold mine properly every single day!

70014.text: I'd forgotten how to put this outfit on, so I created an informative manual! … I won't lose it this time!

70015.text: Fufufu… Why, what a very Bakushin mantle this is!

70019.text: I'll show you the strength of the class president!

71004.text: The school uniform suits me better than anyone else! You guessed it, because I'm the class president!

71008.text: …Indeed! An outfit worthy of being worn by the star of the class!

71009.text: No matter the race… Let's make the Sakura blossoms bloom!

71010.text: School uniforms are sacred garments! I fold mine properly every single day!

71014.text: I'd forgotten how to put this outfit on, so I created an informative manual! … I won't lose it this time!

71015.text: Fufufu… Why, what a very Bakushin mantle this is!

71019.text: I'll show you the strength of the class president!

80000.text: Thank you for your hard work!

81000.text: Fufuu―n… Would you like to challenge the honorable class president!?

81001.text: I've still got more in mee―! I'll show you Bakushin's true strength!

90000.text: Time for a spirited greeting today, as usual! Come on, now, breathe in aaall the way, and… Gooooood morniiiingg――!!

90001.text: Cleaning the blackboard, changing the water in the vases… This class president has been booked since this morning! Truly… I'm just remarkable!

90002.text: Trainer! Greetings! Let's put 100% into our afternoon training, just as we always do―!

90003.text: My energy is at full capacity after having refueled with some lunch! Come, now― training, running, sprinting! Anything you've got, throw it at me, please!

90004.text: Thank you for your hard work today! … Yes, yes! I'm fantastic at thanking people, aren't I!

90005.text: Even when class ends and the bell rings, I'll still keep doing my best! After all, I'm the class president!!

90006.text: No matter how many times I see it, Spring is marvelous… Yes! Because! It is! The class president's! Chosen! Season!!

90007.text: I heard that there are many different ways to eat watermelon. It seems you can eat it with things like salt and sugar… But I'm Team Shove-It-All-in-Your-Face-at-Once!

90008.text: 'Tis the season of many events, including the Holy Hoof Festival. And 'tis the season to show off my skills as class president! Heheh!

90009.text: When it's cold out, please simply gaze upon my smiling face! Because this smile was acclaimed by my very own mother for warming the heart… Cheeese!

91000.text: Nothing out of the ordinary at school today! I've been on patrol with Biko-san, so you can rest easy!

91001.text: The secret to unifying a class? … That is, of course, a brilliant class president!

91002.text: Sometimes I need a reward, you know. I shall praise myself now as such. Good job, me, good job.

91003.text: Bourbon-san and Rice-san are doing their best every single day, and I'm very proud of them! Both of them deserve a gold star!!

91004.text: …Trainer, please say something, anything! Whenever you look me all silent like that… I get the heebie-jeebies!

91005.text: Indeed, I am impossibly flawless! As such, allow me to dance the 3 minute-long choreography you gave me in under a minute!

91006.text: I'll be wearing this outfit for a while! Because whenever I try to take it off, it ends up being quite the challenge!

91007.text: Just as everyone is expecting of me, let's show them this big, shining Sakura blossom together!

91008.text: I shall win every single race! That is why I'm the class president! Iiiindeed!!

91009.text: Lately, I've been meeting Flower-san a lot when I walk to school. Mayhaps, I've drawn her to me with my irresistible charms!

91010.text: Test scores are being posted in the morning? Ha-ha, don't you worry! I'll finish my supplementary lessons straightaway!

91011.text: I finished my homework in two minutes flat! Even without looking at the questions, it was a piece of cake for me!

91012.text: Mother's sakura mochi is aaabsolutely delicious! I'll keep insisting it should be on your shopping list! …Drooool.

91013.text: No matter how hot it is outside, an untidy appearance is a no-go! I refuse to disappoint the diligent pupils who admire the class president so fervently!

91014.text: Around this time of year, I try to read in the moonlight. I heard somewhere that honor students tend to do that.

91015.text: Even if it's cold, I don't wear heavy clothes! Because it's lighter, not to mention faster!

92000.text: Leave the long distance races to me! I'm bound to be good at them someday!

92001.text: I am very fond of sunny days! The reason: because they're easy to run in! That is all for this report! Ehhen!

92002.text: Speed! Explosive power! Class president! I'm made up of all three, but which shall we further develop first?!

92005.text: I'm prepared to be everyone's role model! Because I am the class president!

92006.text: As long as you and I work together, Trainer, we can overcome even the most arduous of trainings with ease!

92007.text: I will not stop until I've set an unprecedented world-record! Bakushin, Bakushiii―n!!

92011.text: As class president! With my whole heart! I shall do my very best!

93000.text: This Sakura that has bloomed with you shall never fall!

93001.text: Fufun, I'll keep on being everyone's role model!

95001.text: Give me the strength to win against any class president, from any world…!!

95003.text: Affirmative, this is Sakura Bakushin O!

95006.text: Have no fear, the class president is here!

110000.text: By all means, go right ahead! Please do train this spectacular talent!

110001.text: Life is an endless cycle of preparing for a lesson and reviewing that lesson! These are the first steps to becoming an honor student!

110002.text: Are you going to Bakushin in a race!?

120000.text: Ooooh! I can feel the power―!

140000.text: Have no fear, the class president is here!

400005.text: Leave the making of sweets to me! I shall be exemplary in all that I do! … Ha! It smells like something's burning!?

400007.text: With the pride of the class president residing in my heart, I shall challenge the competition! …? Why are you looking at me like that?

910100.text: Fufuu―n… Would you like to challenge the honorable class president!?
